== 0.5.0 / 2009-06-17

* added Extname routes
* Controller.uri can now add scheme, host, port

== 0.4.0 / 2009-05-25

Significant internal rework to utilize Tap-0.17.0.
Tap-Server should still be considered experimental.

== 0.3.0 / 2009-03-17

Significant updates.

* added optional REST routes to Tap::Controller
* added persistence wrapper for session root
* significant cleanup
* removed middleware support
* added bindings for running server from
  Firefox/Ubiquity

== 0.2.0 / 2009-03-07

* Reworked server routing to route by ::controller

== 0.1.1 / 2009-02-23

Update executable to use Tap-0.12.2.

== 0.1.0 / 2009-02-17

As of the 0.12.0 release, Tap is distributed as several independent modules.
This is the server module.  In the initial release, the server is working
as a proof-of-principle, and not as a serious interface for tap.
